 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>a</var>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   ; 2; 3; -1; 5; 7; -4 )
  </span>
  - vector function (returns a number with specified index)
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>b</var>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   )  =
   <var>a</var>
   ( 7 −
   <var>n</var>
   )
  </span>
  - transpoze
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>c</var>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   )  =
   <var>a</var>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   )  ·
   <var>b</var>
   (
   <var>n</var>
   )
  </span>
  - dot product
 </p>
