 <p>Matrix</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   ; 11; 12; 13 )
  </span>
  - first row
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   ; 21; 22; 23 )
  </span>
  - second row
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   ; 31; 32; 33 )
  </span>
  - third row
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>M</var>
   (
   <var>i</var>
   ;
   <var>j</var>
   )  =
   <b>take</b>
   (
   <var>i</var>
   ;
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   ) ;
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   ) ;
   <var>R</var>
   <sub>3</sub>
   (
   <var>j</var>
   )  )
  </span>
  - assemble the whole matrix
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>M</var>
   ( 2; 2 )  = 22
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>M</var>
   ( 3; 1 )  = 31
  </span>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>M</var>
   ( 3; 3 )  = 33
  </span>
 </p>
